    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
        }

            .header img {
                height: 50px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-left: 10px;
            }

        .rating {
            color: gold;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .main-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .main-content img {
                max-width: 60%;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

        .card {
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

            .card-header .nav-tabs {
                border: none;
            }

            .card-header .nav-link {
                border: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

                .card-header .nav-link.active {
                    border-bottom: 2px solid black;
                }

        .card-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .price {
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #000;
            border-color: #000;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #333;
                border-color: #333;
            }

        .reviews {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffecec;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .review-card {
            background-color: #f2e1ff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <img src="~/images/logo.png" alt="Logo">
        <h1>FlexDesk</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-content">
            <div>
                <h2>Spark spot <span class="rating">★★★★★</span></h2>
                <img src="~/images/coworking1.jpg" alt="Coworking Space Image">
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <ul class="nav nav-tabs card-header-tabs">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Basic</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#">Standard</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="#">Premium</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title d-flex justify-content-between">
                        <span>Basic fee</span>
                        <span class="price">Price: 20$/h</span>
                    </h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>• Hot Desks: Flexible seating options on a first-come, first-served basis.</li>
                        <li>• Dedicated Desks: Reserved desks for individuals who prefer a consistent spot.</li>
                        <li>• Private Offices: Enclosed offices for teams or individuals needing more privacy.</li>
                        <li>• Meeting Rooms: Bookable spaces for meetings, conferences, or presentations.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block w-100 mt-3">Book your spot</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reviews">
            <h2>Reviews</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="review-card">
                        <p>★★★★★</p>
                        <p>"Fantastic coworking space! The high-speed internet is reliable, and the variety of seating options helps keep my workday flexible and productive. The community events are a great bonus for networking."</p>
                        <p>★★★★★</p>
